\subsection{Sherrington-Kirkpatrick model}
This section presents  results for Sherrington-Kirkpatrick (SK) model, the Ising spin glass on the complete graph.
Figure \ref{fig:FIT} is a plot of ${\overline{q_\infty(N)}}$  
as a function of $N$.  While it is clear that ${\overline{q_\infty(N)}}$ is decreasing with $N$ it is not obvious whether $\overline{q_\infty(N\rightarrow\infty)}$ is zero or greater than zero.  

